---
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, viewport-fit=cover" />
    <title>Terms of Service | VTracer WASM</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Terms of Service for VTracer WASM. Understand usage, disclaimers, and support options." />
    <meta name="color-scheme" content="dark" />
  </head>
  <body class="min-h-screen bg-black text-gray-100">
    <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-10 space-y-8">
      <header class="space-y-2">
        <p class="text-sm text-emerald-400 uppercase tracking-wide">VTracer WASM</p>
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold">Terms of Service</h1>
        <p class="text-gray-400">
          Effective Date: December 8, 2025
        </p>
      </header>

      <section class="space-y-3 text-gray-200 leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          VTracer WASM is provided as a free, client-side tool to convert raster images to SVG using WebAssembly. By using the app at
          <a class="text-emerald-400 hover:text-emerald-300 underline" href="https://jarettrude.github.io/vtracer-wasm/">https://jarettrude.github.io/vtracer-wasm/</a>,
          you agree to these terms.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-3 text-gray-200 leading-relaxed">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-emerald-300">No Warranty</h2>
        <p>
          The app is provided “as-is” without warranties of any kind. Use it at your own risk. You are responsible for verifying outputs and ensuring they meet your needs.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-3 text-gray-200 leading-relaxed">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-emerald-300">Local Processing</h2>
        <p>
          All vectorization happens in your browser. We do not collect or store your images. If you self-host, you are responsible for serving the site securely (HTTPS) to preserve the same guarantees.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-3 text-gray-200 leading-relaxed">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-emerald-300">Acceptable Use</h2>
        <p>
          Do not use VTracer WASM for unlawful purposes or to infringe on intellectual property rights. You are responsible for the content you process.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-3 text-gray-200 leading-relaxed">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-emerald-300">Third-Party Links</h2>
        <p>
          The app may link to third-party sites (e.g., documentation or source repositories). Their content and your use of those sites are governed by
          their own terms of service and privacy policies. Review those before using their services.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-3 text-gray-200 leading-relaxed">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-emerald-300">Updates</h2>
        <p>
          The app may update via its service worker. Continued use after updates constitutes acceptance of the revised terms, which will be dated above.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-3 text-gray-200 leading-relaxed">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-emerald-300">Support & Questions</h2>
        <p>
          For questions, issues, or suggestions, open an issue on GitHub:
          <a class="text-emerald-400 hover:text-emerald-300 underline" href="https://github.com/jarettrude/vtracer-wasm">https://github.com/jarettrude/vtracer-wasm</a>.
        </p>
      </section>

      <footer class="pt-6 border-t border-emerald-800 text-sm text-gray-400">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3">
          <a href="/vtracer-wasm/" class="text-emerald-400 hover:text-emerald-300 underline">Back to App</a>
          <span class="text-gray-600">|</span>
          <a href="/vtracer-wasm/privacy-policy" class="text-emerald-400 hover:text-emerald-300 underline">Privacy Policy</a>
          <span class="text-gray-600">|</span>
          <a href="https://github.com/jarettrude/vtracer-wasm" class="text-emerald-400 hover:text-emerald-300 underline">GitHub</a>
        </div>
      </footer>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
